# CODEOWNERS — `<PROJECT_NAME>`
# 構文: <path-pattern> <@reviewer> [<@reviewer2> ...]
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# === デフォルト ===
*                           @<PROJECT_OWNER>

# === Layer 1：インフラ層（人間が手動でのみ実行）===
/.github/                   @<PROJECT_OWNER>
/.claude/                   @<PROJECT_OWNER>
/supabase/                  @<TECH_OWNER>
/prisma/                    @<TECH_OWNER>
.env*                       @<PROJECT_OWNER>

# === Layer 2：コンテンツ層（意味設計担当の承認必須）===
/lib/prompts/               @<CONTENT_OWNER>
/lib/copy/                  @<CONTENT_OWNER>
/lib/pricing/               @<CONTENT_OWNER>

# === Layer 3：開発層（AI 委任 OK・1 名以上のレビュー）===
/app/                       @<FRONTEND_OWNER>
/components/                @<FRONTEND_OWNER>
/app/api/                   @<TECH_OWNER>
/lib/                       @<TECH_OWNER>
